  "body": "We have some very deep directories both in src and in test. I would be amazing if we could replace\r\n```ts\r\nimport {Libp2pNetwork} from \"../../../../../../src/network\";\r\n```\r\nwith\r\n```ts\r\nimport {Libp2pNetwork} from \"src/network\";\r\n```\r\n```ts\r\nimport {Libp2pNetwork} from \"@network\";\r\n```\r\nor some other variant\r\n\r\nIt's is possible, but we have to find the right setup for us, see\r\n\r\n- https://www.coreycleary.me/escaping-relative-path-hell\r\n- https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/handbook/module-resolution.html",
